# FlavorFit Dashboard Features Documentation

This document provides a comprehensive overview of the features available in the FlavorFit dashboard.

## 1. Dashboard Overview (`/dashboard`)
The main dashboard serves as the central hub, providing users with a high-level view of their nutrition status and quick access to key actions.

### **Features:**
- **Stats Cards**: Real-time tracking of key metrics:
  - **Diet Score**: Overall health score with weekly trend.
  - **Calories Remaining**: Daily calorie countdown.
  - **Energy Trend**: Comparison of energy levels vs. last week.
  - **Recent Reaction**: Alerts for any food sensitivities (e.g., "Dairy sensitivity").
- **Quick Actions**: Shortcuts to common tasks:
  - **Upload Ingredients**: Jump to ingredient analysis.
  - **Generate Diet Plan**: Create a new weekly meal plan.
  - **Ask AI Assistant**: Direct link to the Feedback/AI chat interface.
- **Analytics Charts**:
  - **Weekly Energy**: Line chart showing energy levels Monday-Sunday.
  - **Flavor Profile**: Radar chart visualizing taste preferences (Sweet, Sour, Salty, Bitter, Umami, Spicy).
  - **Nutrition Breakdown**: Bar chart displaying intake of Protein, Carbs, Fats, Fiber, and Vitamins.
- **Recent Meals**: A log of recent activity showing meal name, type (Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner/Snack), calories, status (Completed/Upcoming/Skipped), and time.

---

## 2. Upload Ingredients (`/dashboard/upload`)
An AI-powered tool to identify ingredients from user-uploaded photos and suggest relevant recipes.

### **Features:**
- **Image Upload**: Supports Drag & Drop or file selection for PNG/JPG images (up to 10MB).
- **AI Detection**: Analyzes the image to identify specific ingredients (e.g., "Chicken Breast", "Broccoli").
- **Recipe Generation**: Automatically suggests recipes based on the detected ingredients.
  - Displays **Match Percentage**, **Preparation Time**, and **Calories**.

---

## 3. Recipes (`/dashboard/recipes`)
A personalized recipe discovery hub tailored to the user's taste and dietary goals.

### **Features:**
- **Search & Filter**:
  - text search for specific recipes.
  - **Categories**: Quick filters for "Quick", "High Protein", "Vegan", "Keto", "Gluten-Free".
- **Recipe Cards**: Detailed view for each recipe including:
  - **Match Score**: How well it fits the user's profile.
  - **Quick Stats**: Time, Calories, Difficulty (Easy/Medium/Hard).
  - **Tags**: Health labels (e.g., "High Protein", "Omega-3").
  - **Interactions**: "View Recipe" detail and "Favorite" (Heart) toggle.

---

## 4. Diet Plan (`/dashboard/diet-plan`)
A comprehensive weekly meal planner and nutrition tracker.

### **Features:**
- **Weekly Calendar**: Interactive day selector (Mon-Sun).
- **Nutrition Tracker**: Progress bars for daily goals:
  - **Calories** (kcal)
  - **Protein** (g)
  - **Carbs** (g)
  - **Fat** (g)
- **Meal Timeline**: Chronological list of daily meals (Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner, Snack).
  - **Macro Breakdown**: Per-meal protein, carbs, fat, and calorie counts.
  - **AI Insights**: Notes on health benefits (e.g., "Rich in antioxidants").
  - **Feedback**: Quick button to log feedback for a specific meal.

---

## 5. Feedback / AI Assistant (`/dashboard/feedback`)
An interface for tracking subjective health metrics and training the AI.

### **Features:**
- **Contextual Input**: Text area for detailed user comments on meals.
- **Mood Tracking**: 5-point scale (Bad to Amazing).
- **Energy Level**: Adjustable slider (1-5).
- **Digestion Comfort**: Options ranging from "Uncomfortable" to "Excellent".
- **AI Learning**: Submitting feedback helps the AI personalize future recommendations.

---

## 6. Settings (`/dashboard/settings`)
User preferences and account management.

### **Features:**
- **Profile Management**: Update Full Name and Email; UI for photo change.
- **Notifications**: granular toggles for:
  - Meal reminders
  - Weekly progress reports
  - AI recipe suggestions
- **Dietary Preferences**: Tag-based system to manage restrictions (e.g., "Dairy-Free", "Nut Allergy", "Low Sodium").
- **Account Actions**: Sign Out functionality.
